    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.32.26a" />
                
        <fw type="letterhead">
                Skyrim Farm         <hi rend="caps">JOHN G. NEIHARDT</hi>
            <lb/>
                Route 7
            <lb/>
                Columbia, Mo.
        </fw>
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>6-12-'61</dateline>
                
                
                <salute>Dear Slade:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Yes, that truly <hi rend="underline">is</hi> a personal triumph &#8212; the sort that really makes one happy. It's a pretty safe bet that the youngster will remember you all his life and call you blessed. Not just because he was enabled to graduate; but because a revered person of consequence actually believed in him.</p>
                
                <p>I'm glad we
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.32.26b"/>
                    <fw type="authorial">-2-</fw>
                    <fw type="curatorial"><del/></fw>
                    
                    will not <del/> miss each other. I must give that talk to the picked high school youngsters of the state on the 20th. Then, I hope to get going west in a few days. But I'll plan so as <hi rend="underline">not</hi> to miss you &#8212; Don't trouble about that. I'll not go until I've had a visit with you.</p>
                <closer>
                <salute>Affectionately</salute>
                <signed>John</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <postscript><p>I'm doing 4 videotapes for permanent record &#8212; the first today.</p></postscript>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">26</fw>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
